WEBVTT

00:01:35.740 --> 00:01:40.990 line:80%
[Pursuit of Jade]

00:01:41.170 --> 00:01:43.710 line:80%
[Episode 12]

00:01:43.820 --> 00:01:46.520 line:80%
[Yixiang Restaurant]

00:01:48.390 --> 00:01:50.100 line:80%
Madam Chen!

00:01:51.510 --> 00:01:52.589 line:80%
You are late.

00:01:52.589 --> 00:01:54.650 line:80%
You must drink a penalty drink later.

00:01:56.279 --> 00:01:57.750 line:80%
Madam Chen.

00:01:58.080 --> 00:01:59.430 line:80%
Madam Liu!

00:01:59.720 --> 00:02:02.680 line:80%
Look at Madam Song's outfit today.

00:02:02.870 --> 00:02:05.510 line:80%
She's looking more and more noble.

00:02:05.950 --> 00:02:07.720 line:80%
I'm flattered, Madam Liu.

00:02:07.720 --> 00:02:10.360 line:80%
It is my honor to be invited

00:02:10.380 --> 00:02:12.320 line:80%
by you ladies today.

00:02:15.750 --> 00:02:18.750 line:80%
It's an imperial green jade bracelet!

00:02:19.640 --> 00:02:22.120 line:80%
This is truly hard to come by.

00:02:22.320 --> 00:02:23.640 line:80%
Look at the transparency

00:02:23.640 --> 00:02:24.640 line:80%
and the color.

00:02:25.080 --> 00:02:26.570 line:80%
It must be worth a lot.

00:02:27.590 --> 00:02:28.670 line:80%
Let's talk while we walk.

00:02:28.670 --> 00:02:29.830 line:80%
Come on.

00:02:29.879 --> 00:02:30.760 line:80%
Let's go.

00:02:31.200 --> 00:02:32.310 line:80%
This bracelet is

00:02:32.340 --> 00:02:34.670 line:80%
a greeting gift
from the Magistrate's wife.

00:02:34.670 --> 00:02:36.550 line:80%
No wonder! So it was a gift
from your in-law.

00:02:36.550 --> 00:02:37.490 line:80%
Yes.

00:02:37.840 --> 00:02:39.170 line:80%
-Oh, my.
-My apologies.

00:02:39.480 --> 00:02:40.800 line:80%
You wretched girl!

00:02:41.000 --> 00:02:42.440 line:80%
You... Why are you here?

00:02:44.430 --> 00:02:47.230 line:80%
You didn't follow me here
just to cause trouble, did you?

00:02:47.230 --> 00:02:50.110 line:80%
What? Did you buy this building?

00:02:50.390 --> 00:02:51.920 line:80%
If you can come, why can't I?

00:02:52.390 --> 00:02:53.360 line:80%
Do you know each other?

00:02:53.360 --> 00:02:55.640 line:80%
No. Who would know her?

00:02:56.710 --> 00:02:58.770 line:80%
Madam Liu, let me tell you something.

00:02:58.879 --> 00:03:00.430 line:80%
My son's marriage was

00:03:00.430 --> 00:03:02.360 line:80%
entirely arranged by the Magistrate.

00:03:02.360 --> 00:03:04.810 line:80%
The Magistrate is from a scholarly family.

00:03:05.160 --> 00:03:05.990 line:80%
-Come often if you like it.
-He values

00:03:05.990 --> 00:03:07.320 line:80%
character and upbringing.

00:03:07.320 --> 00:03:09.980 line:80%
The betrothal gifts
followed ancient customs.

00:03:10.230 --> 00:03:13.030 line:80%
But my daughter-in-law brought
a generous dowry.

00:03:13.320 --> 00:03:14.550 line:80%
Marriage is

00:03:14.600 --> 00:03:17.110 line:80%
all about matching social status.

00:03:17.110 --> 00:03:19.440 line:80%
If the character and upbringing are poor,

00:03:19.530 --> 00:03:20.670 line:80%
such a marriage

00:03:20.670 --> 00:03:22.600 line:80%
-shall never take place.
-Indeed.

00:03:22.879 --> 00:03:23.670 line:80%
Right?

00:03:23.870 --> 00:03:25.800 line:80%
The Magistrate is truly generous.

00:03:26.080 --> 00:03:27.080 line:80%
Congratulations

00:03:27.200 --> 00:03:29.710 line:80%
on selling your Scholar Song
for a good price.

00:03:29.710 --> 00:03:30.230 line:80%
You...

00:03:30.230 --> 00:03:30.800 line:80%
Well...

00:03:31.610 --> 00:03:32.840 line:80%
Wretched girl!

00:03:36.120 --> 00:03:37.720 line:80%
Let's go inside quickly.

00:03:37.750 --> 00:03:39.520 line:80%
Don't let such a vulgar person

00:03:39.540 --> 00:03:40.770 line:80%
ruin our mood.

00:03:40.800 --> 00:03:42.160 line:80%
Right? Come on in.

00:03:42.180 --> 00:03:43.450 line:80%
What is she talking about?

00:03:43.450 --> 00:03:45.710 line:80%
Just nonsense. Forget about it.

00:03:47.110 --> 00:03:49.110 line:80%
Here's a toast to you both.

00:03:52.710 --> 00:03:54.920 line:80%
Manager Yu, you are very experienced

00:03:54.920 --> 00:03:56.120 line:80%
in receiving guests.

00:03:56.830 --> 00:03:59.230 line:80%
It seems you have indeed
met a lot of people.

00:04:02.040 --> 00:04:03.690 line:80%
Our restaurant welcomes guests
from everywhere.

00:04:03.690 --> 00:04:05.480 line:80%
We believe harmony brings wealth.

00:04:05.480 --> 00:04:06.600 line:80%
In business,

00:04:06.600 --> 00:04:09.080 line:80%
it's always good to know more people.

00:04:11.920 --> 00:04:13.880 line:80%
Please make yourselves at home, sirs.

00:04:13.880 --> 00:04:16.009 line:80%
I need to go attend to other guests now.

00:04:28.310 --> 00:04:30.110 line:80%
Manager, what's wrong?

00:04:30.480 --> 00:04:31.520 line:80%
You look pale.

00:04:33.750 --> 00:04:35.840 line:80%
The man in there just touched me.

00:04:36.480 --> 00:04:39.050 line:80%
I don't know why, but that single touch

00:04:39.550 --> 00:04:41.390 line:80%
gave me the creeps.

00:04:41.750 --> 00:04:43.810 line:80%
Another guest who tried to grope you?

00:04:44.520 --> 00:04:45.950 line:80%
How shameless.

00:04:46.630 --> 00:04:48.600 line:80%
It's not really about groping.

00:04:49.930 --> 00:04:52.330 line:80%
I feel like I've seen him
somewhere before.

00:04:53.840 --> 00:04:56.570 line:80%
Who was that young lady
we met at the door just now?

00:04:57.250 --> 00:05:00.270 line:80%
She is called Fan Changyu.

00:05:01.070 --> 00:05:04.420 line:80%
She's a famous disaster
from my hometown, Xigu Lane.

00:05:04.770 --> 00:05:06.580 line:80%
The fortune tellers all say

00:05:06.800 --> 00:05:09.670 line:80%
she is a rare jinx
seen only once in a millennium.

00:05:10.480 --> 00:05:12.670 line:80%
She not only caused her parents' deaths,

00:05:12.670 --> 00:05:14.870 line:80%
but her uncle was also killed
because of her.

00:05:14.870 --> 00:05:16.480 line:80%
It even went to court!

00:05:16.540 --> 00:05:17.320 line:80%
By the way,

00:05:17.480 --> 00:05:18.870 line:80%
just in the middle of this month,

00:05:18.870 --> 00:05:21.640 line:80%
a group of bandits
broke into her home at night,

00:05:22.070 --> 00:05:24.110 line:80%
having killed so many people!

00:05:24.110 --> 00:05:27.120 line:80%
Everyone in Lin'an knows about this.

00:05:30.400 --> 00:05:31.590 line:80%
I wonder

00:05:31.870 --> 00:05:33.990 line:80%
how many people have touched her hands

00:05:33.990 --> 00:05:36.510 line:80%
for her to stay so composed

00:05:36.630 --> 00:05:37.990 line:80%
and feel no shame at all.

00:05:38.959 --> 00:05:41.550 line:80%
I've searched everywhere
all these years, yet I failed to find her.

00:05:41.550 --> 00:05:44.959 line:80%
I didn't expect her to be
doing so well in Lin'an,

00:05:45.670 --> 00:05:47.459 line:80%
and to have met so many men.

00:05:51.890 --> 00:05:54.220 line:80%
Perhaps it's just her business dealings.

00:05:55.800 --> 00:05:57.430 line:80%
You are still making excuses for her.

00:05:57.430 --> 00:05:58.570 line:80%
I dare not.

00:05:59.800 --> 00:06:02.310 line:80%
Back then, she left false clues
about her fleeing beyond the pass,

00:06:02.310 --> 00:06:04.910 line:80%
causing me to search
for her in vain for 6 years.

00:06:05.550 --> 00:06:08.590 line:80%
Never thought she'd establish herself
in just 6 years

00:06:09.110 --> 00:06:10.970 line:80%
and open such a large restaurant.

00:06:12.870 --> 00:06:14.670 line:80%
This woman is really something.

00:06:15.110 --> 00:06:15.870 line:80%
Understood.

00:06:16.480 --> 00:06:19.360 line:80%
I will go investigate
her connections immediately.

00:06:19.360 --> 00:06:21.530 line:80%
Also, investigate the men around her.

00:06:21.840 --> 00:06:23.480 line:80%
For anyone who has touched her,

00:06:23.480 --> 00:06:25.740 line:80%
chop off the parts they touched her with,

00:06:25.990 --> 00:06:27.250 line:80%
and present them to me.

00:06:29.390 --> 00:06:30.030 line:80%
Yes.

00:06:30.990 --> 00:06:32.850 line:80%
I will give the orders right away.

00:06:36.730 --> 00:06:39.440 line:80%
Why would Manager Yu
hire someone like that?

00:06:39.600 --> 00:06:40.870 line:80%
In the restaurant business,

00:06:40.870 --> 00:06:42.600 line:80%
nothing's worse than bad luck.

00:06:43.040 --> 00:06:44.840 line:80%
Perhaps Manager Yu

00:06:44.840 --> 00:06:46.970 line:80%
doesn't know this girl's background,

00:06:47.110 --> 00:06:49.170 line:80%
so she let a jinx in.

00:06:50.040 --> 00:06:51.160 line:80%
Madams.

00:06:51.280 --> 00:06:51.940 line:80%
Manager Yu.

00:06:52.010 --> 00:06:53.880 line:80%
What "jinx"?

00:06:55.720 --> 00:06:58.380 line:80%
We don't have such a dish
at Yixiang Restaurant.

00:06:58.670 --> 00:06:59.990 line:80%
Manager Yu,

00:07:00.230 --> 00:07:02.720 line:80%
we are only looking out
for your best interests.

00:07:02.720 --> 00:07:03.990 line:80%
This jinx

00:07:04.160 --> 00:07:05.820 line:80%
can bring death to people.

00:07:06.430 --> 00:07:07.280 line:80%
Really?

00:07:08.640 --> 00:07:10.520 line:80%
But I heard

00:07:10.630 --> 00:07:13.550 line:80%
that she supported
a scholar fiancé for years.

00:07:13.600 --> 00:07:15.150 line:80%
Once the scholar passed
the provincial exam,

00:07:15.150 --> 00:07:17.430 line:80%
he betrayed her
and broke off the engagement.

00:07:17.430 --> 00:07:18.920 line:80%
In my point of view,

00:07:18.960 --> 00:07:20.890 line:80%
the mother and son are the real ingrates

00:07:20.890 --> 00:07:21.840 line:80%
and jinxes.

00:07:22.590 --> 00:07:24.390 line:80%
They not only harmed the young girl

00:07:24.390 --> 00:07:25.890 line:80%
but also her parents.

00:07:29.800 --> 00:07:31.400 line:80%
So this talk of a jinx

00:07:31.480 --> 00:07:34.010 line:80%
might just be a false rumor.

00:07:34.550 --> 00:07:36.150 line:80%
You're right, Madam Liu.

00:07:36.670 --> 00:07:37.910 line:80%
Mrs. Fan

00:07:37.940 --> 00:07:39.990 line:80%
not only takes care of her sister
all by herself.

00:07:39.990 --> 00:07:41.840 line:80%
Since she joined our Yixiang Restaurant,

00:07:41.840 --> 00:07:43.040 line:80%
my braised meat business

00:07:43.040 --> 00:07:44.530 line:80%
has been booming.

00:07:44.840 --> 00:07:45.990 line:80%
I think

00:07:45.990 --> 00:07:48.250 line:80%
she's actually an auspicious blessing!

00:07:50.360 --> 00:07:51.560 line:80%
However, Madam Song,

00:07:52.070 --> 00:07:54.870 line:80%
who told you she was a jinx?

00:07:59.020 --> 00:08:02.180 line:80%
Just some gossip, I suppose.

00:08:03.960 --> 00:08:05.040 line:80%
Why do women

00:08:05.060 --> 00:08:07.040 line:80%
have to make things hard for other women?

00:08:07.040 --> 00:08:09.040 line:80%
Spouting nonsense and gossiping all day

00:08:09.040 --> 00:08:11.040 line:80%
will bring about God's punishment.

00:08:11.960 --> 00:08:13.570 line:80%
As educated and reasonable
as you are, Madam Song,

00:08:13.570 --> 00:08:16.340 line:80%
how could you gossip
like some filthy trash?

00:08:16.420 --> 00:08:18.360 line:80%
You must have been deceived.

00:08:24.360 --> 00:08:26.600 line:80%
Why are there
still some dishes not served?

00:08:26.600 --> 00:08:27.660 line:80%
I'll go check on them.

00:08:27.660 --> 00:08:29.360 line:80%
Madams, please enjoy the food.

00:08:29.360 --> 00:08:29.960 line:80%
Okay.

00:08:43.800 --> 00:08:44.710 line:80%
You know what?

00:08:44.920 --> 00:08:46.320 line:80%
This manager

00:08:47.070 --> 00:08:49.280 line:80%
got pregnant out of wedlock.

00:08:49.590 --> 00:08:50.830 line:80%
Who knows whose bastard

00:08:50.830 --> 00:08:53.190 line:80%
she carried in her belly?

00:08:54.520 --> 00:08:58.280 line:80%
"Why do women have to make things
hard for other women?" Ridiculous.

00:08:58.280 --> 00:08:59.710 line:80%
I think she's obviously

00:08:59.710 --> 00:09:01.140 line:80%
an immoral slut

00:09:01.350 --> 00:09:03.520 line:80%
just like Fan Changyu.

00:09:05.470 --> 00:09:06.410 line:80%
Let's

00:09:06.440 --> 00:09:07.760 line:80%
not let other people's gossip

00:09:07.760 --> 00:09:09.590 line:80%
ruin our mood.

00:09:09.800 --> 00:09:10.810 line:80%
Yes, exactly.

00:09:10.920 --> 00:09:12.450 line:80%
Let's get back to the point.

00:09:22.830 --> 00:09:25.020 line:80%
A bunch of noisy gossips.

00:09:25.640 --> 00:09:27.220 line:80%
According to them,

00:09:27.430 --> 00:09:29.970 line:80%
the child might be hiding
in this restaurant.

00:09:33.120 --> 00:09:34.580 line:80%
The one who talks the most,

00:09:35.350 --> 00:09:36.640 line:80%
teach her a lesson.

00:09:40.400 --> 00:09:41.130 line:80%
Understood.

00:09:41.920 --> 00:09:44.160 line:80%
-Madam Liu.
-Do you think I'm drunk?

00:09:44.160 --> 00:09:45.070 line:80%
You drank too much.

00:09:45.070 --> 00:09:48.000 line:80%
For this matter,
please put in a good word for me

00:09:48.310 --> 00:09:52.370 line:80%
-in front of your son's father-in-law.
-Don't worry. Just leave it to me.

00:10:06.270 --> 00:10:08.290 line:80%
"Bring about God's punishment"?

00:10:10.830 --> 00:10:13.160 line:80%
I think the one to suffer God's punishment

00:10:13.240 --> 00:10:15.640 line:80%
s-should be that wretched girl!

00:10:15.800 --> 00:10:17.280 line:80%
If God

00:10:17.280 --> 00:10:18.960 line:80%
really sees us all,

00:10:19.470 --> 00:10:21.640 line:80%
He should make that wretched girl...

00:10:36.290 --> 00:10:39.310 line:80%
You'd better think twice
before you speak nonsense

00:10:39.950 --> 00:10:41.520 line:80%
and watch your mouth.

00:10:42.130 --> 00:10:43.730 line:80%
If you spout nonsense again,

00:10:44.050 --> 00:10:45.920 line:80%
it won't end as easily as today.

00:10:46.860 --> 00:10:47.610 line:80%
O-Okay.

00:10:47.630 --> 00:10:49.210 line:80%
I-I get it.

00:10:53.760 --> 00:10:54.430 line:80%
Madam.

00:10:55.040 --> 00:10:55.710 line:80%
Madam!

00:10:56.590 --> 00:10:57.240 line:80%
Madam!

00:11:08.170 --> 00:11:09.210 line:80%
[Braised pork tongue]

00:11:09.230 --> 00:11:11.230 line:80%
[Braised pork belly]

00:11:11.310 --> 00:11:17.090 line:80%
[Fan's Braised Meat Shop]

00:11:12.830 --> 00:11:14.240 line:80%
Are there any pig ears left?

00:11:14.240 --> 00:11:15.240 line:80%
None left today.

00:11:15.260 --> 00:11:16.860 line:80%
You may come again tomorrow.

00:11:18.080 --> 00:11:19.770 line:80%
It's almost New Year.

00:11:19.830 --> 00:11:20.760 line:80%
Our braised meat is

00:11:20.760 --> 00:11:21.950 line:80%
selling better and better.

00:11:21.950 --> 00:11:23.400 line:80%
You've worked really hard.

00:11:23.400 --> 00:11:24.550 line:80%
You're the one working hard,

00:11:24.550 --> 00:11:26.470 line:80%
busy with so many things every day.

00:11:26.470 --> 00:11:28.190 line:80%
Making money is never easy.

00:11:28.830 --> 00:11:29.830 line:80%
However,

00:11:29.830 --> 00:11:31.830 line:80%
although our braised meat is selling well,

00:11:31.830 --> 00:11:33.950 line:80%
if we want to take it to the next level,

00:11:33.950 --> 00:11:36.640 line:80%
we could design an emblem
for our braised meat.

00:11:36.710 --> 00:11:37.520 line:80%
An emblem?

00:11:38.830 --> 00:11:42.260 line:80%
But my braised meat is
either sliced and served on a plate,

00:11:42.710 --> 00:11:45.070 line:80%
or wrapped in oil paper for takeout.

00:11:45.350 --> 00:11:46.800 line:80%
What's the use of an emblem?

00:11:46.800 --> 00:11:48.400 line:80%
It's exceptionally useful.

00:11:49.400 --> 00:11:50.200 line:80%
Come out here.

00:11:52.920 --> 00:11:54.270 line:80%
[Fan's Braised Meat Shop]

00:11:53.280 --> 00:11:54.120 line:80%
Look

00:11:54.590 --> 00:11:56.560 line:80%
at these shops downstairs from mine.

00:11:56.560 --> 00:11:57.770 line:80%
Fang's tea,

00:11:57.800 --> 00:11:58.880 line:80%
Li's wine.

00:11:58.530 --> 00:11:59.550 line:80%
[Luo's Pawnshop]

00:11:58.880 --> 00:12:00.670 line:80%
Doesn't every shop have an emblem?

00:11:59.650 --> 00:12:00.230 line:80%
[Fang's Tea Shop]

00:12:00.230 --> 00:12:01.020 line:80%
[Fang]

00:12:00.880 --> 00:12:03.010 line:80%
And each one is unique.

00:12:01.100 --> 00:12:02.420 line:80%
[Li]

00:12:02.470 --> 00:12:04.240 line:80%
[Hua San]

00:12:03.120 --> 00:12:05.190 line:80%
You can tell whose shop it is at a glance.

00:12:05.190 --> 00:12:07.350 line:80%
Later, think of a design for your emblem.

00:12:07.350 --> 00:12:09.590 line:80%
You can make a banner
to hang by the signboard,

00:12:09.590 --> 00:12:11.070 line:80%
so people can see it from afar.

00:12:11.070 --> 00:12:12.400 line:80%
And make some more oil paper.

00:12:12.400 --> 00:12:14.070 line:80%
Print the emblem on the oil paper, too.

00:12:14.070 --> 00:12:15.120 line:80%
When someone buys braised meat,

00:12:15.120 --> 00:12:16.220 line:80%
wrap it in that oil paper.

00:12:16.220 --> 00:12:18.550 line:80%
Your fame will surely surpass the Wang's.

00:12:19.160 --> 00:12:19.800 line:80%
I got it.

00:12:20.070 --> 00:12:22.040 line:80%
I'll find you

00:12:22.040 --> 00:12:23.670 line:80%
a scholar with nice handwriting.

00:12:23.670 --> 00:12:25.350 line:80%
Let's get this done today.

00:12:26.130 --> 00:12:26.880 line:80%
Qianqian.

00:12:26.340 --> 00:12:27.610 line:80%
[Fan's Braised Meat Shop]

00:12:27.760 --> 00:12:30.070 line:80%
My husband can write as well.

00:12:30.240 --> 00:12:31.640 line:80%
I'll just ask him to help.

00:12:32.040 --> 00:12:34.820 line:80%
How is your husband's handwriting?

00:12:35.040 --> 00:12:36.000 line:80%
Excellent.

00:12:36.670 --> 00:12:37.470 line:80%
Really.

00:12:38.800 --> 00:12:40.730 line:80%
Even more beautiful than his face.

00:12:41.880 --> 00:12:43.280 line:80%
That impressive?

00:12:43.590 --> 00:12:45.280 line:80%
Then he must be as great
as the legendary calligraphers,

00:12:45.280 --> 00:12:46.640 line:80%
Wang Xizhi and Zhong Yao!

00:12:46.640 --> 00:12:47.430 line:80%
Wang Xi...

00:12:50.980 --> 00:12:53.880 line:80%
I don't know who those two are,

00:12:54.430 --> 00:12:56.230 line:80%
but I think he's about that good.

00:12:57.070 --> 00:12:58.070 line:80%
Changyu,

00:12:58.470 --> 00:12:59.760 line:80%
I really love

00:12:59.830 --> 00:13:01.120 line:80%
your personality.

00:13:01.820 --> 00:13:05.510 line:80%
[Fan]

00:13:08.470 --> 00:13:10.950 line:80%
Sir, your handwriting is truly elegant.

00:13:11.070 --> 00:13:12.760 line:80%
-Yes.
-Having worked here for years,

00:13:12.760 --> 00:13:14.310 line:80%
I've never seen anyone's handwriting

00:13:14.310 --> 00:13:16.350 line:80%
as good as yours, sir.

00:13:16.390 --> 00:13:17.510 line:80%
Truly amazing.

00:13:17.640 --> 00:13:19.840 line:80%
-It's so well written.
-Manager, look.

00:13:21.900 --> 00:13:23.360 line:80%
[Fan]

00:13:23.670 --> 00:13:24.830 line:80%
It's so beautiful.

00:13:26.760 --> 00:13:28.220 line:80%
Do you want to take a break?

00:13:28.720 --> 00:13:30.360 line:80%
No need. I'll keep writing.

00:13:30.920 --> 00:13:31.670 line:80%
Changyu.

00:13:32.590 --> 00:13:34.390 line:80%
Your husband's handwriting...

00:13:34.880 --> 00:13:36.220 line:80%
It's really good!

00:13:37.180 --> 00:13:38.840 line:80%
Much better than that Wang...

00:13:39.830 --> 00:13:41.640 line:80%
Wang something.

00:13:41.640 --> 00:13:44.400 line:80%
Fine. Beauty is in the eye
of the beholder.

00:13:44.400 --> 00:13:45.400 line:80%
Of course it's good.

00:13:45.400 --> 00:13:48.070 line:80%
Yes. No matter what Zheng writes or draws,

00:13:48.070 --> 00:13:49.860 line:80%
I think it's the best.

00:13:50.830 --> 00:13:52.830 line:80%
Fuling, take Changning upstairs
to have some goodies.

00:13:52.830 --> 00:13:54.490 line:80%
You can eat whatever you want.

00:13:54.590 --> 00:13:56.190 line:80%
Thank you, Fairy Sister.

00:13:56.670 --> 00:13:57.950 line:80%
That's so sweet.

00:13:58.240 --> 00:13:58.840 line:80%
Off you go.

00:14:02.350 --> 00:14:03.310 line:80%
Changyu,

00:14:03.470 --> 00:14:04.640 line:80%
you really found yourself

00:14:04.640 --> 00:14:06.970 line:80%
a husband good with both brains and brawn.

00:14:07.070 --> 00:14:08.470 line:80%
Thank you for the compliment.

00:14:08.470 --> 00:14:09.530 line:80%
No need to thank me.

00:14:10.190 --> 00:14:11.470 line:80%
From today on,

00:14:11.640 --> 00:14:13.470 line:80%
we must stick together.

00:14:13.590 --> 00:14:15.280 line:80%
Show those gossips

00:14:15.430 --> 00:14:18.290 line:80%
that we young women are
also capable of great deeds!

00:14:21.070 --> 00:14:26.650 line:80%
[Fan]

00:14:24.760 --> 00:14:26.950 line:80%
-I want some, too!
-I also want some!

00:14:26.790 --> 00:14:29.150 line:80%
[Fan's Braised Meat Shop]

00:14:26.950 --> 00:14:29.550 line:80%
Me too! I want one!

00:14:34.560 --> 00:14:37.790 line:80%
[Fan]

00:14:40.520 --> 00:14:42.280 line:80%
Qianqian, you're so insightful.

00:14:42.280 --> 00:14:43.940 line:80%
You said drawing these things

00:14:44.000 --> 00:14:46.160 line:80%
would attract a lot of people,
and it really did!

00:14:46.160 --> 00:14:47.670 line:80%
You're mistaken.

00:14:47.830 --> 00:14:49.240 line:80%
The real attraction is

00:14:49.240 --> 00:14:50.680 line:80%
your husband.

00:14:51.960 --> 00:14:54.180 line:80%
[Fan's Braised Meat Shop]

00:15:03.430 --> 00:15:04.760 line:80%
Why are you still standing there?

00:15:04.760 --> 00:15:05.760 line:80%
Go help him.

00:15:06.350 --> 00:15:07.240 line:80%
Go, go, go.

00:15:14.000 --> 00:15:14.830 line:80%
I'll help you.

00:15:18.920 --> 00:15:19.650 line:80%
Here you are.

00:15:25.120 --> 00:15:26.850 line:80%
Isn't this the meat you wanted?

00:15:34.760 --> 00:15:36.160 line:80%
This was just wrapped up.

00:15:36.430 --> 00:15:37.120 line:80%
Yes.

00:15:39.950 --> 00:15:41.120 line:80%
Is what he takes different?

00:15:41.120 --> 00:15:43.450 line:80%
Yes, the meat he hands over smells better.

00:15:45.350 --> 00:15:46.640 line:80%
-I want some, too!
-I also want some!

00:15:46.640 --> 00:15:47.740 line:80%
Give it to me! Me!

00:15:50.640 --> 00:15:52.830 line:80%
That's mine! Give it to me!
I want some, too!

00:15:52.830 --> 00:15:53.710 line:80%
Here you are.

00:15:54.070 --> 00:15:54.950 line:80%
Here.

00:15:58.880 --> 00:16:02.180 line:80%
You can do it.

00:16:02.310 --> 00:16:05.380 line:80%
Come on.

00:16:06.880 --> 00:16:08.880 line:80%
It's fine. It's okay.

00:16:12.160 --> 00:16:13.760 line:80%
You weighed this wrong.

00:16:15.640 --> 00:16:16.810 line:80%
No rush, sir.

00:16:17.000 --> 00:16:18.000 line:80%
No need to rush.

00:16:27.830 --> 00:16:28.890 line:80%
It's underweight.

00:16:29.040 --> 00:16:30.170 line:80%
I cut an extra piece.

00:16:31.280 --> 00:16:32.010 line:80%
Here you are.

00:16:41.160 --> 00:16:42.520 line:80%
What does it have to do with you?

00:16:42.520 --> 00:16:43.800 line:80%
Stay out of this.

00:16:47.280 --> 00:16:50.640 line:80%
-I want some, too!
-I also want some!

00:16:50.670 --> 00:16:52.070 line:80%
-Me, too.
-Any meat left?

00:16:53.950 --> 00:16:55.610 line:80%
I shouldn't have let you come.

00:17:00.630 --> 00:17:04.070 line:80%
-Give it to me. I'll pay double the price.
-I also want some!

00:17:04.070 --> 00:17:05.909 line:80%
-I want some, too.
-Me, too.

00:17:10.210 --> 00:17:17.830 line:80%
[Fan's Braised Meat Shop]

00:17:18.869 --> 00:17:19.869 line:80%
Is there any left?

00:17:20.240 --> 00:17:21.070 line:80%
Sorry, sir.

00:17:21.070 --> 00:17:22.470 line:80%
We're sold out for today.

00:17:23.350 --> 00:17:24.950 line:80%
What about those in the back?

00:17:25.070 --> 00:17:26.280 line:80%
Those are just scraps.

00:17:26.280 --> 00:17:27.480 line:80%
Scraps are fine, too.

00:17:27.480 --> 00:17:29.010 line:80%
Are you selling them or not?

00:17:29.240 --> 00:17:30.700 line:80%
Yes. If you pay, I'll sell.

00:17:30.760 --> 00:17:31.680 line:80%
Here, take it.

00:17:34.760 --> 00:17:36.000 line:80%
Your hands are greasy.

00:17:36.000 --> 00:17:38.200 line:80%
Be careful not to dirty the paper on top.

00:17:46.060 --> 00:17:46.620 line:80%
[Fan]

00:17:48.350 --> 00:17:49.930 line:80%
This calligraphy is brilliant.

00:17:49.930 --> 00:17:51.190 line:80%
Using it to wrap meat is

00:17:51.480 --> 00:17:52.960 line:80%
squandering a treasure.

00:17:53.870 --> 00:17:54.520 line:80%
[Fan]

00:17:55.030 --> 00:17:55.790 line:80%
Really nice.

00:17:58.960 --> 00:18:00.870 line:80%
"Squandering a treasure"?

00:18:02.870 --> 00:18:04.070 line:80%
What does that mean?

00:18:09.040 --> 00:18:09.840 line:80%
Let's pack up.

00:18:13.360 --> 00:18:18.030 line:80%
[Welcome guests from far and wide]

00:18:16.480 --> 00:18:17.800 line:80%
I'm not drunk.

00:18:22.280 --> 00:18:23.440 line:80%
Take care, Mr. Wu.

00:18:25.280 --> 00:18:26.440 line:80%
Qianqian.

00:18:27.870 --> 00:18:29.480 line:80%
Go wait for me in the carriage.

00:18:29.480 --> 00:18:31.280 line:80%
Did you enjoy your drink, Mr. Wu?

00:18:31.630 --> 00:18:33.830 line:80%
It's getting late. It's time to go home.

00:18:34.680 --> 00:18:36.510 line:80%
Why go home?

00:18:37.800 --> 00:18:39.400 line:80%
Everyone knows I am

00:18:39.910 --> 00:18:41.750 line:80%
a regular here.

00:18:42.200 --> 00:18:43.260 line:80%
-Mr. Wu.
-Let's go.

00:18:43.280 --> 00:18:44.440 line:80%
Drink a few more cups with me.

00:18:44.440 --> 00:18:46.680 line:80%
I'm doing this for your own good.

00:18:46.870 --> 00:18:48.680 line:80%
If you go back late,

00:18:48.680 --> 00:18:49.800 line:80%
Mrs. Wu will come cause trouble

00:18:49.800 --> 00:18:51.730 line:80%
for our Yixiang Restaurant again.

00:18:56.040 --> 00:18:58.680 line:80%
Don't use that fierce woman
to pressure me.

00:18:58.720 --> 00:19:00.010 line:80%
Listen carefully.

00:19:00.200 --> 00:19:02.540 line:80%
If you don't keep me good company today,

00:19:02.560 --> 00:19:05.620 line:80%
don't expect to keep this place
running smoothly.

00:19:05.720 --> 00:19:07.910 line:80%
Mr. Wu, please mind your manners.

00:19:08.350 --> 00:19:09.040 line:80%
Go away!

00:19:11.350 --> 00:19:14.040 line:80%
How dare you, a maid,
talk to me like that?

00:19:14.480 --> 00:19:15.630 line:80%
-Who taught you to do that?
-Mr. Wu!

00:19:15.630 --> 00:19:16.200 line:80%
Mr. Wu.

00:19:16.200 --> 00:19:17.040 line:80%
Calm down, please.

00:19:17.040 --> 00:19:18.310 line:80%
I'll drink with you.

00:19:20.240 --> 00:19:21.240 line:80%
Bring the cups.

00:19:28.680 --> 00:19:29.350 line:80%
Cheers.

00:19:36.220 --> 00:19:37.170 line:80%
How dare you,

00:19:37.680 --> 00:19:39.240 line:80%
a scoundrel, run wild here?

00:19:39.350 --> 00:19:41.070 line:80%
I've dealt with countless men like you.

00:19:41.070 --> 00:19:41.960 line:80%
Send him back to the Wu's Mansion

00:19:41.960 --> 00:19:43.000 line:80%
and hand him over to Mrs. Wu!

00:19:43.000 --> 00:19:43.590 line:80%
Yes.

00:19:44.800 --> 00:19:45.480 line:80%
Let go!

00:19:46.040 --> 00:19:47.590 line:80%
Who do you think you are?

00:19:48.110 --> 00:19:49.870 line:80%
Let go! Let go of me!

00:19:50.390 --> 00:19:51.780 line:80%
Do you know who I am?

00:20:00.240 --> 00:20:01.080 line:80%
Bitch!

00:20:45.630 --> 00:20:46.690 line:80%
Are you alright?

00:20:59.720 --> 00:21:00.870 line:80%
Here you are, Mr. Qi.

00:21:05.590 --> 00:21:07.520 line:80%
Master, what should we do with him?

00:21:09.280 --> 00:21:10.800 line:80%
Do as Manager Yu said.

00:21:11.000 --> 00:21:13.400 line:80%
Send him back
to Mrs. Wu at the Wu's Mansion.

00:21:13.590 --> 00:21:16.000 line:80%
Remember, send him back alive.

00:21:17.240 --> 00:21:19.240 line:80%
Don't cause trouble for Manager Yu.

00:21:19.350 --> 00:21:20.480 line:80%
-Yes!
-Understood.

00:21:31.760 --> 00:21:34.550 line:80%
Manager Yu, you look pale.

00:21:36.710 --> 00:21:38.370 line:80%
Were you frightened just now?

00:21:43.870 --> 00:21:44.550 line:80%
I'm fine.

00:21:45.930 --> 00:21:47.680 line:80%
Thank you for saving me, Mr. Qi.

00:22:00.440 --> 00:22:01.150 line:80%
Farewell.

00:22:53.310 --> 00:22:55.440 line:80%
Manager, are you okay?

00:23:02.040 --> 00:23:03.700 line:80%
He behaves a bit like that guy,

00:23:04.440 --> 00:23:06.170 line:80%
but there's no scar on his face.

00:23:07.840 --> 00:23:09.640 line:80%
And the voice is different, too.

00:23:11.550 --> 00:23:12.810 line:80%
Don't scare yourself.

00:23:13.280 --> 00:23:14.850 line:80%
Why would he come to Lin'an?

00:23:15.350 --> 00:23:16.310 line:80%
Who?

00:23:19.610 --> 00:23:20.330 line:80%
Nothing.

00:23:27.560 --> 00:23:29.600 line:80%
[Permeating fragrance]

00:23:27.800 --> 00:23:29.480 line:80%
These snacks are all for you.

00:23:29.830 --> 00:23:31.680 line:80%
My sister can really eat as well.

00:23:32.040 --> 00:23:34.110 line:80%
She eats enough for 3 meals
in one sitting,

00:23:34.110 --> 00:23:36.310 line:80%
with her rice bowl as big
as a soup tureen.

00:23:36.310 --> 00:23:38.240 line:80%
Your sister is impressive!

00:23:38.550 --> 00:23:40.480 line:80%
Have you ever seen a pig slaughter?

00:23:40.720 --> 00:23:41.480 line:80%
No.

00:23:42.150 --> 00:23:43.560 line:80%
My sister can knock a pig out

00:23:43.560 --> 00:23:45.720 line:80%
with one single slap.

00:23:46.910 --> 00:23:47.690 line:80%
Really?

00:23:47.800 --> 00:23:48.520 line:80%
I've never seen anyone

00:23:48.520 --> 00:23:50.180 line:80%
as formidable as your sister.

00:23:50.760 --> 00:23:52.930 line:80%
Fuling, come over and help!

00:23:53.760 --> 00:23:55.450 line:80%
I'm going out for a bit.

00:23:55.740 --> 00:23:56.960 line:80%
I'll be right back.

00:24:41.000 --> 00:24:41.910 line:80%
Thief!

00:24:42.390 --> 00:24:44.000 line:80%
I... I'm not a thief.

00:24:44.070 --> 00:24:45.160 line:80%
I don't care who you are.

00:24:45.160 --> 00:24:46.350 line:80%
You are stealing food.

00:24:46.350 --> 00:24:48.630 line:80%
I'm going to tell my sister
and the Fairy Sister.

00:24:48.630 --> 00:24:49.240 line:80%
Don't!

00:24:49.240 --> 00:24:51.390 line:80%
Changyu, someone is stealing food!

00:24:52.910 --> 00:24:54.280 line:80%
Don't, please don't!

00:24:54.280 --> 00:24:55.870 line:80%
It's all because you're stealing food!

00:24:55.870 --> 00:24:57.000 line:80%
This is my home.

00:24:57.000 --> 00:24:58.910 line:80%
My mother owns this restaurant.

00:24:58.960 --> 00:25:00.400 line:80%
Why can't I eat it?

00:25:00.480 --> 00:25:02.910 line:80%
You are the Fairy Sister's son?

00:25:03.570 --> 00:25:06.080 line:80%
What's your name? How old are you?

00:25:07.070 --> 00:25:09.200 line:80%
I'm Yu Bao'er. I'm 6.

00:25:09.200 --> 00:25:10.060 line:80%
What about you?

00:25:10.440 --> 00:25:11.800 line:80%
Try this piece.

00:25:12.000 --> 00:25:13.630 line:80%
Just this piece is enough for me.

00:25:13.630 --> 00:25:15.250 line:80%
Mother doesn't let me eat too much.

00:25:15.250 --> 00:25:17.710 line:80%
She says too many sweets cause cavities.

00:25:18.440 --> 00:25:19.770 line:80%
What are cavities?

00:25:20.110 --> 00:25:21.230 line:80%
They're like...

00:25:24.590 --> 00:25:26.760 line:80%
Little worms will eat your teeth.

00:25:26.960 --> 00:25:28.550 line:80%
It hurts so much.

00:25:28.720 --> 00:25:30.270 line:80%
Worms will grow?

00:25:30.630 --> 00:25:33.720 line:80%
Like cabbage worms or rice weevils?

00:25:34.070 --> 00:25:35.270 line:80%
I don't know, either.

00:25:35.380 --> 00:25:36.600 line:80%
I've never had them.

00:25:37.150 --> 00:25:39.010 line:80%
Then we'd better not eat anymore.

00:25:40.050 --> 00:25:42.180 line:80%
How about we go play outside together?

00:25:43.850 --> 00:25:45.710 line:80%
Mother says I have a special fate,

00:25:46.000 --> 00:25:47.800 line:80%
and I should avoid seeing too many people.

00:25:47.800 --> 00:25:48.600 line:80%
Only then...

00:25:49.020 --> 00:25:50.420 line:80%
Only then can I stay safe.

00:25:53.280 --> 00:25:56.390 line:80%
Then let's play hide-and-seek.

00:26:12.960 --> 00:26:14.090 line:80%
You can't take this.

00:26:14.960 --> 00:26:16.090 line:80%
-Kids...
-Go away.

00:26:16.110 --> 00:26:17.320 line:80%
-Sorry.
-I'm sorry.

00:26:26.460 --> 00:26:27.380 line:80%
Bao'er?

00:26:28.350 --> 00:26:29.550 line:80%
Why are you here?

00:26:29.590 --> 00:26:30.630 line:80%
-This way.
-Let's go.

00:26:30.630 --> 00:26:32.760 line:80%
Your mother told you not to run around!

00:26:34.040 --> 00:26:35.830 line:80%
You two. Don't touch it.

00:26:45.830 --> 00:26:47.170 line:80%
It doesn't matter.

00:26:47.240 --> 00:26:49.440 line:80%
-Just a moment.
-OK, I'll go back later.

00:26:51.590 --> 00:26:53.320 line:80%
Where did you come from, brats?

00:26:53.520 --> 00:26:55.250 line:80%
You spoiled my mood. Get out.

00:26:55.630 --> 00:26:57.110 line:80%
You're still running here?

00:26:57.110 --> 00:26:57.800 line:80%
Stop!

00:26:58.150 --> 00:26:58.830 line:80%
Run!

00:26:59.880 --> 00:27:01.840 line:80%
You brats, how dare you ruin my day?

00:27:01.870 --> 00:27:02.760 line:80%
Get lost!

00:27:10.480 --> 00:27:11.240 line:80%
Changning?

00:27:12.200 --> 00:27:13.070 line:80%
Changning!

00:27:28.550 --> 00:27:29.410 line:80%
She's not here.

00:27:52.440 --> 00:27:54.720 line:80%
I'll go in and light the lamps
for you two first.

00:27:54.720 --> 00:27:56.850 line:80%
No need to light the lamps in this room.

00:27:57.040 --> 00:27:59.520 line:80%
Arrange the wine and dishes
the same as on our first day here.

00:27:59.520 --> 00:28:00.150 line:80%
Got it.

00:28:17.070 --> 00:28:18.070 line:80%
Keep this in mind.

00:28:19.110 --> 00:28:20.600 line:80%
No matter when or where,

00:28:21.480 --> 00:28:23.410 line:80%
never make decisions on my behalf,

00:28:24.550 --> 00:28:26.350 line:80%
even if we kill the wrong person.

00:28:27.960 --> 00:28:29.090 line:80%
Do you understand?

00:28:30.440 --> 00:28:31.070 line:80%
Yes.

00:28:34.200 --> 00:28:36.200 line:80%
I'm so sleepy.

00:28:36.200 --> 00:28:37.410 line:80%
Shh. Be quiet.

00:28:38.590 --> 00:28:40.390 line:80%
How is the investigation going?

00:28:41.960 --> 00:28:43.310 line:80%
I've asked around.

00:28:44.180 --> 00:28:46.380 line:80%
Based on the time she arrived in Lin'an,

00:28:46.870 --> 00:28:50.270 line:80%
the child was very likely conceived
in the Prince's Mansion.

00:28:50.630 --> 00:28:53.390 line:80%
To confirm her identity
with absolute certainty,

00:28:53.390 --> 00:28:56.520 line:80%
we need the Nanny to come to Lin'an
to verify it in person.

00:29:07.680 --> 00:29:08.940 line:80%
Then go arrange it now.

00:29:09.720 --> 00:29:11.120 line:80%
I'll get on it right away.

00:29:12.000 --> 00:29:12.730 line:80%
Who's there?

00:29:25.870 --> 00:29:27.480 line:80%
Sold out so early?

00:29:28.240 --> 00:29:29.040 line:80%
All sold out for today.

00:29:29.040 --> 00:29:30.640 line:80%
Please come again tomorrow.

00:29:30.760 --> 00:29:31.280 line:80%
Okay.

00:29:40.480 --> 00:29:41.110 line:80%
Make way.

00:29:42.200 --> 00:29:42.870 line:80%
Move.

00:29:44.760 --> 00:29:47.590 line:80%
Mr. Li, where are these soldiers from?

00:29:48.760 --> 00:29:50.960 line:80%
Advisor Guo,
who freeloaded here yesterday, said

00:29:50.960 --> 00:29:53.640 line:80%
the front lines are in trouble,
so they're requisitioning grain again.

00:29:53.640 --> 00:29:54.520 line:80%
Looks like

00:29:55.440 --> 00:29:57.480 line:80%
these soldiers are here for the grain.

00:29:57.480 --> 00:29:59.480 line:80%
Wei Xuan's bound to be defeated.

00:29:59.590 --> 00:30:03.390 line:80%
I just didn't expect that he couldn't even
hold on until the New Year.

00:30:06.760 --> 00:30:07.680 line:80%
I also heard

00:30:08.350 --> 00:30:10.040 line:80%
that in Chongzhou,
in order to collect grain,

00:30:10.040 --> 00:30:11.760 line:80%
they drove farmers to their deaths.

00:30:11.760 --> 00:30:13.440 line:80%
They all say Mr. He in our Jizhou is

00:30:13.440 --> 00:30:15.040 line:80%
a just and upright official.

00:30:15.040 --> 00:30:16.590 line:80%
I hope he won't be like those
in Chongzhou,

00:30:16.590 --> 00:30:17.830 line:80%
just to collect grain,

00:30:17.830 --> 00:30:20.230 line:80%
driving the common people to their deaths.

00:30:21.720 --> 00:30:24.980 line:80%
It all depends on
how the Jizhou Government will handle it.

00:30:32.110 --> 00:30:33.040 line:80%
What is this for?

00:30:33.800 --> 00:30:34.460 line:80%
It's yours.

00:30:36.150 --> 00:30:37.680 line:80%
I don't need it. You keep it.

00:30:38.550 --> 00:30:39.520 line:80%
No.

00:30:40.240 --> 00:30:41.300 line:80%
Half for each of us.

00:30:41.440 --> 00:30:43.500 line:80%
You wrote hundreds of paper packets.

00:30:44.440 --> 00:30:46.000 line:80%
I might lose it if I carry it.

00:30:47.080 --> 00:30:48.170 line:80%
You keep it for me.

00:30:52.240 --> 00:30:54.480 line:80%
Fine. I'll keep it for you.

00:30:55.870 --> 00:30:56.390 line:80%
Okay.

00:30:59.830 --> 00:31:01.230 line:80%
Have you seen Changning?

00:31:03.280 --> 00:31:04.280 line:80%
She's missing.

00:31:05.240 --> 00:31:07.570 line:80%
Those goddamn bandits are after us again?

00:31:10.830 --> 00:31:11.910 line:80%
-Bao'er!
-Changning!

00:31:11.910 --> 00:31:12.480 line:80%
Bao'er!

00:31:12.480 --> 00:31:13.390 line:80%
Who is Bao'er?

00:31:13.520 --> 00:31:14.350 line:80%
My son.

00:31:15.760 --> 00:31:16.350 line:80%
Fuling!

00:31:17.200 --> 00:31:17.910 line:80%
Fuling!

00:31:18.480 --> 00:31:20.440 line:80%
Manager, Bao'er isn't in the secret room.

00:31:20.440 --> 00:31:21.800 line:80%
Changning was just here.

00:31:21.800 --> 00:31:23.040 line:80%
I went out for a bit,

00:31:23.040 --> 00:31:24.070 line:80%
and she's gone.

00:31:25.520 --> 00:31:26.310 line:80%
Qi...

00:31:26.870 --> 00:31:28.250 line:80%
It must be him.

00:31:28.310 --> 00:31:29.460 line:80%
Who is Qi?

00:31:29.720 --> 00:31:31.120 line:80%
That man comes every day.

00:31:31.310 --> 00:31:32.000 line:80%
Every time I see him,

00:31:32.000 --> 00:31:33.310 line:80%
I get goosebumps.

00:31:33.310 --> 00:31:34.760 line:80%
He must be the one who took Bao'er away!

00:31:34.760 --> 00:31:36.220 line:80%
Let's split up and search.

00:31:36.240 --> 00:31:36.830 line:80%
Okay.

00:31:41.150 --> 00:31:42.240 line:80%
Has that guest surnamed Qi left?

00:31:42.240 --> 00:31:43.450 line:80%
I-I don't know.

00:31:46.040 --> 00:31:47.800 line:80%
Manager, please calm down.

00:31:49.150 --> 00:31:50.350 line:80%
Where is that guy surnamed Qi?

00:31:50.350 --> 00:31:51.750 line:80%
He just left not long ago.

00:31:52.720 --> 00:31:54.680 line:80%
Did he have anyone with him when he left?

00:31:54.680 --> 00:31:56.220 line:80%
He left in a hurry.

00:31:56.310 --> 00:31:57.170 line:80%
I didn't notice

00:31:57.200 --> 00:31:58.740 line:80%
whether he had anyone with him.

00:31:58.740 --> 00:31:59.440 line:80%
-Manager!
-Manager!

00:31:59.440 --> 00:32:00.500 line:80%
Calm down, please!

00:32:11.720 --> 00:32:13.180 line:80%
Manager, are you alright?

00:32:13.870 --> 00:32:14.590 line:80%
How is your hand?

00:32:14.590 --> 00:32:15.520 line:80%
Let me see.

00:32:45.040 --> 00:32:46.440 line:80%
I'll get on it right away.

00:32:47.150 --> 00:32:47.880 line:80%
Who's there?

00:32:49.240 --> 00:32:50.800 line:80%
Sir, it's me.

00:32:57.190 --> 00:32:58.720 line:80%
Sorry, sir.

00:32:58.870 --> 00:33:00.870 line:80%
I accidentally knocked over
the lampstand just now.

00:33:00.870 --> 00:33:01.870 line:80%
Did I disturb you?

00:33:02.240 --> 00:33:02.970 line:80%
Give it to me.

00:33:03.480 --> 00:33:04.150 line:80%
You can go now.

00:33:04.150 --> 00:33:05.080 line:80%
Enjoy your meal.

00:33:10.950 --> 00:33:17.660 line:80%
[Heaven-class]

00:33:15.480 --> 00:33:16.830 line:80%
How have I taught you?

00:33:18.110 --> 00:33:19.970 line:80%
I... I dare not forget, Mother.

00:33:21.000 --> 00:33:21.720 line:80%
I was just...

00:33:21.720 --> 00:33:22.550 line:80%
Just what?

00:33:23.240 --> 00:33:24.440 line:80%
Just playing around?

00:33:26.480 --> 00:33:27.550 line:80%
Do you just let everything

00:33:27.550 --> 00:33:29.040 line:80%
I usually tell you go in one ear
and out the other?

00:33:29.040 --> 00:33:30.000 line:80%
Why won't you listen?

00:33:30.000 --> 00:33:31.260 line:80%
Why are you so playful?

00:33:35.150 --> 00:33:37.040 line:80%
Qianqian, your hand is hurt.

00:33:37.440 --> 00:33:39.500 line:80%
Why don't you go apply some medicine?

00:33:40.820 --> 00:33:45.350 line:80%
[Heaven-class]

00:33:43.020 --> 00:33:45.470 line:80%
Fairy Sister, please don't be mad.

00:33:45.960 --> 00:33:47.760 line:80%
It's my fault. I fell asleep.

00:33:48.040 --> 00:33:50.270 line:80%
Bao'er was just keeping me company.

00:33:52.680 --> 00:33:53.800 line:80%
I won't blame you.

00:33:54.440 --> 00:33:57.380 line:80%
Can I come play with Bao'er again
in the future?

00:34:08.080 --> 00:34:09.740 line:80%
Get up now. The ground is cold.

00:34:14.030 --> 00:34:14.780 line:80%
Mother.

00:34:14.709 --> 00:34:17.530 line:80%
[Heaven-class]

00:34:19.910 --> 00:34:22.350 line:80%
Qianqian is usually so nice to everyone.

00:34:22.950 --> 00:34:25.550 line:80%
But why does she treat her own son
like an enemy?

00:34:25.600 --> 00:34:26.830 line:80%
Her reaction today was

00:34:26.830 --> 00:34:28.630 line:80%
indeed more fearful than yours.

00:34:30.280 --> 00:34:31.939 line:80%
I'm going back to check on her.

00:34:32.510 --> 00:34:34.830 line:80%
Even close friends have their secrets.

00:34:35.200 --> 00:34:37.130 line:80%
She will tell you when she wants to.

00:34:37.870 --> 00:34:40.130 line:80%
I wonder what Qianqian has been through.

00:34:44.030 --> 00:34:46.560 line:80%
Changyu, I'm sleepy.

00:34:48.160 --> 00:34:49.030 line:80%
She's sleepy.

00:34:52.310 --> 00:34:53.439 line:80%
Come on, Changning.

00:34:57.240 --> 00:34:58.030 line:80%
Hold onto me.

00:35:04.840 --> 00:35:09.160 line:80%
[He]

00:35:09.270 --> 00:35:16.530 line:80%
[Peace at the border]

00:35:09.500 --> 00:35:11.580 line:80%
In our Great Yin's 1 capital city
and 17 prefectures,

00:35:11.580 --> 00:35:13.510 line:80%
the Northwest comprises 4 of them.

00:35:13.720 --> 00:35:16.380 line:80%
Jinzhou is barren,
and Chongzhou has rebelled.

00:35:16.640 --> 00:35:19.570 line:80%
That leaves only 2 prefectures,
Jizhou and Yanzhou.

00:35:20.030 --> 00:35:20.870 line:80%
Yanzhou is

00:35:21.690 --> 00:35:22.970 line:80%
a garrison post.

00:35:23.910 --> 00:35:25.910 line:80%
The Imperial Court strictly forbids
hoarding grain or farming there.

00:35:25.910 --> 00:35:27.870 line:80%
That means right now in the Northwest,

00:35:27.870 --> 00:35:30.400 line:80%
only our Jizhou prefecture
can supply grain.

00:35:31.280 --> 00:35:32.410 line:80%
Wei Xuan

00:35:33.160 --> 00:35:35.080 line:80%
clearly thinks the fire of war
in Chongzhou is

00:35:35.080 --> 00:35:36.370 line:80%
not raging enough.

00:35:36.830 --> 00:35:40.260 line:80%
Wei Xuan sent troops
to requisition grain by force.

00:35:40.350 --> 00:35:43.010 line:80%
The soldiers even took the seeds
farmers kept.

00:35:43.430 --> 00:35:45.840 line:80%
Forget about spring planting
of the common people.

00:35:45.480 --> 00:35:49.170 line:80%
[He]

00:35:46.120 --> 00:35:49.480 line:80%
It'll already be a blessing for them
to just survive the harsh winter.

00:35:49.480 --> 00:35:50.600 line:80%
Doing this is

00:35:50.680 --> 00:35:52.390 line:80%
like digging our own grave!

00:35:56.160 --> 00:35:58.290 line:80%
Why couldn't we collect enough grain?

00:35:59.200 --> 00:36:00.660 line:80%
I've had it investigated.

00:36:01.160 --> 00:36:01.950 line:80%
A month ago,

00:36:01.950 --> 00:36:03.310 line:80%
a group of merchants from out of town

00:36:03.310 --> 00:36:05.080 line:80%
bought up grain everywhere at high prices.

00:36:05.080 --> 00:36:07.600 line:80%
The people only kept seeds
and coarse grain for themselves,

00:36:07.600 --> 00:36:08.830 line:80%
and sold all the rest.

00:36:09.310 --> 00:36:10.830 line:80%
Buying grain in wartime.

00:36:11.560 --> 00:36:14.290 line:80%
Go investigate these merchants
from out of town.

00:36:14.680 --> 00:36:16.410 line:80%
-Yes, General.
-Yes, General.

00:36:18.900 --> 00:36:20.560 line:80%
Your Lordship, I've figured it out.

00:36:20.560 --> 00:36:21.990 line:80%
The one who bought grain in the city is

00:36:21.990 --> 00:36:23.430 line:80%
the manager of Lin'an Rice Shop,

00:36:23.430 --> 00:36:24.290 line:80%
named Zhao Xun.

00:36:26.430 --> 00:36:28.080 line:80%
He united grain merchants from many places

00:36:28.080 --> 00:36:29.800 line:80%
to buy grain at high prices
in Yanzhou and Jizhou,

00:36:29.800 --> 00:36:31.660 line:80%
totaling nearly 200,000 piculs.

00:36:32.390 --> 00:36:33.440 line:80%
Zhao Xun?

00:36:37.470 --> 00:36:39.640 line:80%
Has he been
closely interacting with someone recently?

00:36:39.640 --> 00:36:42.240 line:80%
Yes, someone who claimed
to be a rice merchant from the Capital,

00:36:42.240 --> 00:36:43.200 line:80%
surnamed Qi.

00:36:44.510 --> 00:36:45.470 line:80%
Qi?

00:36:48.390 --> 00:36:49.280 line:80%
Mr. Qi,

00:36:49.560 --> 00:36:51.800 line:80%
our manager hasn't recovered
from her cold yet.

00:36:51.800 --> 00:36:53.600 line:80%
She has been resting behind closed doors

00:36:53.600 --> 00:36:55.560 line:80%
and really can't see anyone.

00:36:55.990 --> 00:36:57.790 line:80%
Hope you can understand it, sir.

00:37:00.160 --> 00:37:01.410 line:80%
If it's a cold,

00:37:02.080 --> 00:37:02.840 line:80%
why didn't she accept

00:37:02.840 --> 00:37:05.120 line:80%
the medicine I had a famous doctor
prescribe for her?

00:37:05.120 --> 00:37:06.990 line:80%
She didn't even accept the fox-fur coat.

00:37:06.990 --> 00:37:08.590 line:80%
Is it not warm enough for her?

00:37:09.870 --> 00:37:10.870 line:80%
Or is it that

00:37:11.430 --> 00:37:13.630 line:80%
your manager is avoiding me on purpose?

00:37:14.560 --> 00:37:15.350 line:80%
No way.

00:37:15.720 --> 00:37:17.800 line:80%
Our manager doesn't mean to slight you.

00:37:17.800 --> 00:37:19.550 line:80%
She is just seriously ill.

00:37:20.830 --> 00:37:21.950 line:80%
How serious?

00:37:22.870 --> 00:37:24.330 line:80%
She's not dead yet, is she?

00:37:26.870 --> 00:37:27.800 line:80%
Tell her,

00:37:28.240 --> 00:37:30.870 line:80%
I always get to see the person
I want to see.

00:37:36.080 --> 00:37:37.800 line:80%
So it's you, Mr. Qi! Welcome.

00:37:38.080 --> 00:37:40.120 line:80%
Go serve the dishes. The best ones.

00:37:40.800 --> 00:37:41.390 line:80%
Yes.

00:37:45.200 --> 00:37:46.930 line:80%
Serve the most expensive ones.

00:37:49.800 --> 00:37:51.000 line:80%
It seems you're fine.

00:37:59.350 --> 00:38:00.470 line:80%
It's just a cold.

00:38:00.600 --> 00:38:01.600 line:80%
Nothing serious.

00:38:02.510 --> 00:38:05.600 line:80%
Besides, the physician said
it's more important to keep inner peace.

00:38:05.600 --> 00:38:07.290 line:80%
Don't get angry or sad,

00:38:07.680 --> 00:38:09.080 line:80%
and avoid looking at disgusting things.

00:38:09.080 --> 00:38:10.540 line:80%
That helps with recovery.

00:38:18.280 --> 00:38:18.940 line:80%
Don't move.

00:38:20.770 --> 00:38:21.870 line:80%
Men and women aren't supposed to
get intimate.

00:38:21.870 --> 00:38:23.730 line:80%
Please show some respect, Mr. Qi.

00:38:23.870 --> 00:38:24.930 line:80%
I said, don't move.

00:38:39.510 --> 00:38:40.830 line:80%
Your pulse was slow just now.

00:38:40.830 --> 00:38:42.230 line:80%
It's indeed like a chill.

00:38:43.240 --> 00:38:45.280 line:80%
But now it has quickened a lot.

00:38:53.870 --> 00:38:56.120 line:80%
This medicine is exactly what you need.

00:38:59.280 --> 00:39:00.280 line:80%
Thank you, Mr. Qi.

00:39:01.160 --> 00:39:03.800 line:80%
Manager Yu, you seem
to dislike me so much.

00:39:08.830 --> 00:39:10.310 line:80%
What are you talking about?

00:39:10.310 --> 00:39:12.160 line:80%
It's not that I dislike you.

00:39:12.680 --> 00:39:14.510 line:80%
It's just that I haven't recovered
from my cold,

00:39:14.510 --> 00:39:16.120 line:80%
and I'm afraid I'll spoil your mood

00:39:16.120 --> 00:39:17.780 line:80%
for enjoying the delicacies.

00:39:18.560 --> 00:39:19.890 line:80%
I'll take my leave then.

00:39:25.200 --> 00:39:26.330 line:80%
Where are you going?

00:39:27.390 --> 00:39:28.600 line:80%
None of your business.

00:39:28.600 --> 00:39:30.030 line:80%
I wanted you to take the medicine

00:39:30.030 --> 00:39:31.280 line:80%
for your own good.

00:39:32.350 --> 00:39:34.310 line:80%
There are plenty of men who care about me.

00:39:34.310 --> 00:39:35.170 line:80%
Go wait in line.

00:39:36.830 --> 00:39:37.640 line:80%
Who are they?

00:39:38.990 --> 00:39:39.930 line:80%
Let go.

00:39:40.200 --> 00:39:40.910 line:80%
Let go of me!

00:39:41.910 --> 00:39:42.970 line:80%
What are you doing?

00:39:43.640 --> 00:39:46.510 line:80%
Mr. Qi's concern for Manager Yu is

00:39:46.510 --> 00:39:48.060 line:80%
truly a grand gesture.

00:39:48.280 --> 00:39:50.470 line:80%
He actually booked
the entire Yixiang Restaurant.

00:39:50.470 --> 00:39:51.160 line:80%
Manager Yu,

00:39:51.600 --> 00:39:53.240 line:80%
now you can have a good rest.

00:39:55.830 --> 00:39:57.760 line:80%
You booked my Yixiang Restaurant?

00:39:57.870 --> 00:39:59.080 line:80%
Manager Zhao just said

00:39:59.080 --> 00:40:00.800 line:80%
he'd offer 100 taels a day

00:40:00.800 --> 00:40:02.350 line:80%
to book the Yixiang Restaurant
for 10 days.

00:40:02.350 --> 00:40:03.280 line:80%
Ten days.

00:40:03.830 --> 00:40:05.280 line:80%
I'm booking everything

00:40:05.950 --> 00:40:07.480 line:80%
in the Yixiang Restaurant.

00:40:10.870 --> 00:40:12.830 line:80%
Only 100 taels a day?

00:40:13.950 --> 00:40:15.770 line:80%
Did you not bring enough money?

00:40:16.030 --> 00:40:17.310 line:80%
At least 1,000 taels a day.

00:40:17.310 --> 00:40:18.200 line:80%
Not a wen less.

00:40:18.950 --> 00:40:20.150 line:80%
Do you have that much?

00:40:22.600 --> 00:40:23.600 line:80%
Just this little?

00:40:29.010 --> 00:40:32.650 line:80%
[Yixiang Restaurant]

00:40:31.120 --> 00:40:32.160 line:80%
That's strange.

00:40:32.200 --> 00:40:33.310 line:80%
How weird.

00:40:34.140 --> 00:40:36.150 line:80%
The Manager didn't notify us.

00:40:38.990 --> 00:40:41.430 line:80%
-Excuse me.
-The Restaurant is closed to reorganize.

00:40:41.430 --> 00:40:43.640 line:80%
We appreciate your understanding.

00:40:42.730 --> 00:40:46.140 line:80%
[The Restaurant is closed to reorganize.
We appreciate your understanding.]

00:40:46.910 --> 00:40:48.640 line:80%
Why is it closed all of a sudden?

00:40:48.800 --> 00:40:49.930 line:80%
Where is Manager Yu?

00:40:50.640 --> 00:40:52.160 line:80%
We also came to work early this morning

00:40:52.160 --> 00:40:53.430 line:80%
and just found out.

00:40:53.720 --> 00:40:55.250 line:80%
We haven't seen Manager Yu.

00:40:55.910 --> 00:40:56.800 line:80%
This is weird.

00:40:59.200 --> 00:41:00.510 line:80%
Madam Man, Mr. Li.

00:41:00.910 --> 00:41:02.560 line:80%
Why is the Yixiang Restaurant closed?

00:41:02.560 --> 00:41:04.220 line:80%
Mr. Qi booked the whole place.

00:41:04.280 --> 00:41:06.020 line:80%
He sent us back to rest for a few days,

00:41:06.020 --> 00:41:07.390 line:80%
saying he doesn't need us to serve.

00:41:07.390 --> 00:41:08.520 line:80%
It's weird, though.

00:41:08.560 --> 00:41:09.760 line:80%
Even the doors are all locked.

00:41:09.760 --> 00:41:10.990 line:80%
In all my years at the Yixiang Restaurant,

00:41:10.990 --> 00:41:12.530 line:80%
I've never seen this happen before.

00:41:12.530 --> 00:41:13.290 line:80%
Indeed.

00:41:13.950 --> 00:41:14.880 line:80%
Where is Qianqian?

00:41:14.880 --> 00:41:15.800 line:80%
She was sick yesterday,

00:41:15.800 --> 00:41:16.800 line:80%
so she must be inside now.

00:41:16.800 --> 00:41:17.520 line:80%
Yes.

00:41:18.720 --> 00:41:19.780 line:80%
I'll go take a look.

00:41:20.200 --> 00:41:21.160 line:80%
The doors are locked.

00:41:21.160 --> 00:41:23.560 line:80%
You're not actually thinking of flying...

00:41:28.240 --> 00:41:29.570 line:80%
She actually flew over.

00:41:33.680 --> 00:41:34.430 line:80%
Qianqian!

00:41:36.280 --> 00:41:36.990 line:80%
Qianqian!

00:41:38.950 --> 00:41:39.950 line:80%
-Qianqian!
-Don't come over!

00:41:39.950 --> 00:41:40.760 line:80%
Help!

00:41:41.800 --> 00:41:43.560 line:80%
Don't come over. Stay back.

00:41:46.120 --> 00:41:47.180 line:80%
-Qianqian.
-No...

00:41:47.460 --> 00:41:48.220 line:80%
No.

00:41:49.580 --> 00:41:50.510 line:80%
-No!
-Qianqian.

00:41:50.870 --> 00:41:51.480 line:80%
Get lost!

00:41:51.990 --> 00:41:53.340 line:80%
-Qianqian.
-Go away!

00:41:54.680 --> 00:41:55.500 line:80%
No!

00:41:55.680 --> 00:41:56.390 line:80%
No!

00:41:58.560 --> 00:41:59.200 line:80%
Changyu...

00:41:59.200 --> 00:42:00.090 line:80%
It's okay.

00:42:04.080 --> 00:42:04.990 line:80%
What's wrong?

00:42:05.120 --> 00:42:05.870 line:80%
What dream did you have

00:42:05.870 --> 00:42:07.000 line:80%
to scare you so much?

00:42:09.000 --> 00:42:10.570 line:80%
I dreamed of a madman.

00:42:14.680 --> 00:42:15.610 line:80%
Go away!

00:42:15.630 --> 00:42:17.080 line:80%
A masked madman.

00:42:25.240 --> 00:42:25.970 line:80%
Here you are.

00:42:29.310 --> 00:42:30.600 line:80%
Madam Man said the Yixiang Restaurant was

00:42:30.600 --> 00:42:32.500 line:80%
booked by Mr. Qi.

00:42:32.910 --> 00:42:33.990 line:80%
What's going on?

00:42:38.350 --> 00:42:39.030 line:80%
No.

00:42:39.910 --> 00:42:41.910 line:80%
I didn't dare take on this business.

00:42:43.200 --> 00:42:43.990 line:80%
Why?

00:42:45.030 --> 00:42:46.910 line:80%
I deliberately asked for 1,000 taels,

00:42:46.910 --> 00:42:48.200 line:80%
but he still agreed.

00:42:49.600 --> 00:42:51.350 line:80%
The more I thought about it,
the more scared I got.

00:42:51.350 --> 00:42:53.950 line:80%
So I just closed up the restaurant
to avoid him.

00:42:56.510 --> 00:42:58.080 line:80%
Is it possible

00:42:58.560 --> 00:43:00.570 line:80%
that he just likes you?

00:43:05.870 --> 00:43:06.870 line:80%
I don't know.

00:43:08.310 --> 00:43:10.030 line:80%
I just feel like

00:43:10.640 --> 00:43:11.840 line:80%
it's not that simple.

00:43:13.950 --> 00:43:15.680 line:80%
How about I tie him up in a sack,

00:43:15.680 --> 00:43:16.430 line:80%
beat him up,

00:43:16.430 --> 00:43:17.630 line:80%
and ask what he wants?

00:43:18.600 --> 00:43:20.910 line:80%
Beating people up isn't
a long-term solution.

00:43:20.910 --> 00:43:23.080 line:80%
Isn't Butcher Guo the best example?

00:43:24.280 --> 00:43:26.880 line:80%
Besides,
booking a restaurant isn't illegal.

00:43:29.430 --> 00:43:30.430 line:80%
That makes sense.

00:43:31.600 --> 00:43:33.600 line:80%
Why is this clingy guy so annoying?

00:43:35.080 --> 00:43:38.280 line:80%
I've seen enough
of this domineering, big-spending act.

00:43:39.800 --> 00:43:41.720 line:80%
If he really just likes me,

00:43:42.200 --> 00:43:44.200 line:80%
and I want him to give up completely,

00:43:44.200 --> 00:43:46.400 line:80%
I must sever his emotional attachment.

00:43:49.390 --> 00:43:50.950 line:80%
I have to let him know

00:43:51.510 --> 00:43:53.170 line:80%
that I already have a husband,

00:43:53.310 --> 00:43:54.720 line:80%
so he doesn't stand a chance.

00:43:54.720 --> 00:43:56.320 line:80%
But you don't have a husband.

00:43:56.390 --> 00:43:57.430 line:80%
You do.

00:43:57.640 --> 00:43:59.280 line:80%
I do, but you don't.